<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><em>League of Legends</em>-based free-to-play tag fighting game <em><a title="Games > 2XKO [22 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/2xko">2XKO</a></em> will add Thresh as a playable character alongside the <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/2xko-adds-senna-on-june-9">previously announced</a> Senna on June 9, developer <a title="Companies > Riot Games [53 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/riot-games">Riot Games</a> announced. <span id="more-1053744"></span></p><p><em>2XKO</em> is available now in for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>Thresh Gameplay Reveal Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Thresh Gameplay Reveal Trailer | 2XKO" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/45q18ujEYyk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
